  <h1>Launch Roadmap — to Dec 19, 2026</h1>
  <div class="sub">Solo founder + AI · Full platform (SMB marketplace + Corporate M&amp;A) · ~26 weeks</div>
  <div class="countdown">🚀 Launch day: <b>Sat 19 Dec 2026</b> · ~<b>26 weeks</b> from today (Jun 18)</div>

  <div class="mission">
    <div class="k">North star</div>
    <p>Go from a hardened MVP to a fully launched, paid, two-sided M&amp;A platform — corporates closing deals and entrepreneurs buying businesses — live and earning revenue on Dec 19.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="phases">
    <div class="phase"><span class="tp">P0 · Jun–Jul</span><div class="mo" style="margin-top:6px;">Foundation</div><h3>Lock &amp; validate</h3><div class="ms">Finish incorporation, lock architecture, harden MVP, 20 interviews, waitlist 100+, brand/domain.</div></div>
    <div class="phase"><span class="tp">P1 · Aug</span><div class="mo" style="margin-top:6px;">Build I</div><h3>SMB marketplace</h3><div class="ms">Listings, seller onboarding, buyer discovery, AI health score, Aria + pgvector matching, Razorpay listing fees.</div></div>
    <div class="phase"><span class="tp">P2 · Sep</span><div class="mo" style="margin-top:6px;">Build II</div><h3>Corporate M&amp;A</h3><div class="ms">Deal pipeline (drag-drop), deal rooms, valuation tools, DD checklists, SaaS subscriptions, target screening.</div></div>
    <div class="phase"><span class="tp">P3 · Oct</span><div class="mo" style="margin-top:6px;">Trust</div><h3>Transactions</h3><div class="ms">Aadhaar eSign, escrow, GST invoicing, verified listings, advisor marketplace, WhatsApp + email.</div></div>
    <div class="phase"><span class="tp">P4 · Nov</span><div class="mo" style="margin-top:6px;">Scale</div><h3>Mobile + harden</h3><div class="ms">React Native parity, push, security audit, analytics/big-data base, load testing, closed beta.</div></div>
    <div class="phase launch"><span class="tp">P5 · Dec</span><div class="mo" style="margin-top:6px;">Launch</div><h3>🚀 Go live Dec 19</h3><div class="ms">Waitlist beta, bug bash, marketing assets, PR, launch runbook, public GA + GTM blast.</div></div>
  </div>

